            <bug_when>2009-10-01 09:09:55 +0200</bug_when>
            <thetext>At the moment all qooxdoo widgets use the qooxdoo ScrollBar widget to render scrollbars. Since there are still situations where we cannot use the qooxdoo qidgets and the native widgets are still used there can be a mix of two different scrollbar styles in an application. This could be avoided if we there was a way to tell an application to use native scrollbars instead of qooxdoo scrollbars everywhere.</thetext>
